Yawma hum AAal_a_ a*l*nn_a_ri yuftanoon*a*
_Th_ooqoo fitnatakum h_atha_ alla_th_ee kuntum bihi tastaAAjiloon*a*
Inna almuttaqeena fee jann_a_tin waAAuyoon*in*
