Wafee anfusikum afal_a_ tub_s_iroon*a*
Wafee a*l*ssam_a_-i rizqukum wam_a_ tooAAadoon*a*
Fawarabbi a*l*ssam_a_-i wa*a*l-ar_d_i innahu la_h_aqqun mithla m_a_ annakum tan_t_iqoon*a*
Hal at_a_ka _h_adeethu _d_ayfi ibr_a_heema almukrameen*a*
I_th_ dakhaloo AAalayhi faq_a_loo sal_a_man q_a_la sal_a_mun qawmun munkaroon*a*
Far_a_gha il_a_ ahlihi faj_a_a biAAijlin sameen*in*
Faqarrabahu ilayhim q_a_la al_a_ ta\kuloon*a*
