Faaqbalati imraatuhu fee _s_arratin fa_s_akkat wajhah_a_ waq_a_lat AAajoozun AAaqeem*un*
Q_a_loo ka_tha_liki q_a_la rabbuki innahu huwa al_h_akeemu alAAaleem*u*
Q_a_la fam_a_ kha_t_bukum ayyuh_a_ almursaloon*a*
Q_a_loo inn_a_ orsiln_a_ il_a_ qawmin mujrimeen*a*
Linursila AAalayhim _h_ij_a_ratan min _t_een*in*
Musawwamatan AAinda rabbika lilmusrifeen*a*
Faakhrajn_a_ man k_a_na feeh_a_ mina almu\mineen*a*
Fam_a_ wajadn_a_ feeh_a_ ghayra baytin mina almuslimeen*a*
Watarakn_a_ feeh_a_ _a_yatan lilla_th_eena yakh_a_foona alAAa_tha_ba al-aleem*a*
Wafee moos_a_ i_th_ arsa*l*n_a_hu il_a_ firAAawna bisul_ta_nin mubeen*in*
Fatawall_a_ biruknihi waq_a_la s_ah_irun aw majnoon*un*
Faakha_th_n_a_hu wajunoodahu fanaba_th_n_a_hum fee alyammi wahuwa muleem*un*
Wafee AA_a_din i_th_ arsaln_a_ AAalayhimu a*l*rree_h_a alAAaqeem*a*
M_a_ ta_th_aru min shay-in atat AAalayhi ill_a_ jaAAalat-hu ka*al*rrameem*i*
Wafee thamooda i_th_ qeela lahum tamattaAAoo _h_att_a_ _h_een*in*
FaAAataw AAan amri rabbihim faakha_th_at-humu a*l*_ssa_AAiqatu wahum yan\_th_\uroon*a*
